Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Fitted and ready to go options

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Set within the highly successful master planned 'Emerald Lakes' community, opportunities exist to lease high quality office space. The Town Centre commercial building consists of 4 levels of office space and is surrounded by residential and retail buildings.

Available options;
* 315 sqm- ground floor, fully fitted, high quality tenancy including furniture and workstations. 

* 364sqm- Level 3, full high quality fitout in place, great natural light and views all around.

* 150-387sqm- Level 3, open plan tenancy which can be split to suit. Fitout incentives on offer.

* 200-413sqm- Level 4, open plan tenancy which can be split to suit. Fitout incentives on offer.

* 1,067sqm- Level 5, exclusive whole top floor. Full corporate fitout in place including furniture. Great views and natural light throughout. 

All fitted tenancies are cabled with fibre connected and ready to occupy immediately.
Ample allocated car parking onsite for both staff and clients within basement and on-grade.
3d walkthroughs available in link for all fitted tenancies.

For further information including plans or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agent.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: MULTIPLE OPTIONS AND NEW TERMS AVAILABLE
